ISLAMABAD, Jul 03 (APP):Minister for Information and Broadcasting Senator Shibli Faraz Friday expressed grief and sorrow over the loss of lives in train accident in Sheikhupura.
In a statement, he expressed his heartfelt condolences to the grieved families of Sikh Yatris over the loss of precious lives. He prayed for the early recovery of the injured.
